column2: select objID, clean, u, g, r, i , z, u_err, g_err, r_err, i_err, z_err, ra, dec, ra_err, dec_err, RowNumber from (select objID, clean, psfMag_u - extinction_u as u, psfMag_g - extinction_g as g, psfMag_r - extinction_R as r, psfMag_i - extinction_i as i, psfMag_z - extinction_z as z, psfMagErr_u as u_err, psfMagErr_g as g_err, psfMagErr_r as r_err, psfMagErr_i as i_err, psfMagErr_z as z_err, ra, dec, raErr as ra_err, decErr as dec_err, ROW_NUMBER () over (order by dec) as RowNumber from star as s) as OS where OS.RowNumber % # = # AND OS.CLEAN = # AND OS.ra BETWEEN # AND # AND OS.dec BETWEEN # AND # AND OS.psfMag_r < # AND OS.psfMag_g < #
